# Checks

One-time environment (slopcop from PyPI via lockfile):

```bash
uv sync --all-packages --group dev
```

Backend: `pnpm run check:be` (Ruff lint, Ruff format, ty, slopcop via `uv run slopcop`).

Frontend: `pnpm run check:fe`.

Combined: `pnpm run check:fast`.

Ruff autofix:

```bash
uv run ruff check --fix h_arcane arcane_builtins arcane_cli arcane_infra tests scripts
uv run ruff format h_arcane arcane_builtins arcane_cli arcane_infra tests scripts
```
